{
  "stem": "294.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I want you to know that my city had a very large population of ethnic Germans who identified with Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think they prepared the ground very well for the German occupation forces.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they were all traitors, all these Germans who lived in the city of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, in November, the very beginning of November, we lived upstairs on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother, I remember distinctly-- she went downstairs, because our janitor downstairs was sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he asked my mother to come down and see what's wrong with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She wasn't home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was alone, and there was a knock on the door, or a doorbell rang-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I opened the door, and there were three Germans-- one in a green uniform-- the Schutzpolizei, or whatever-- and two in black uniforms of the so-called Volksdeutschen, who I described before.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Those were the ethnic Germans who right away took over, you know-- they helped the occupation forces right away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said that-- where is my mother?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, my mother is downstairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, she probably-- people heard some commotion and let her know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- she came upstairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, you are arrested for political reasons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know-- and the term-- the term deportation was not known in those days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was-- there was no precedent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were the first ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We really thought we were arrested-- for what reasons, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Germans said, put all your valuables on the table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put a few warm things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and, by the way, they said that I was not on the list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother said, oh, go to your boyfriend, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
